com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz

Class HalfTrade

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.Notification
      • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.HalfTrade

  • public class HalfTrade
extends Notification
    ~~DESCRIPTION: We're going to have half a trade involved in this class. Our application is completely dedicated around various users trading their skills to one another, similarily to the trade class we're going to have this class focus ESPECIALLY on each half of the trade that is going on at any given point of time! Neither Trade nor HalfTrade use notifyD because their commit methods are called by TradesList and Trade, respectively.
